---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for IsItAuDHD.com. Learn how we handle your data, quiz answers, and email information."
>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-text-light mb-8">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-text-light leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">The Short Version</h2>
        <p>
          Your quiz answers never leave your device. We don't track you across the web.
          If you give us your email, we only use it to send you what you asked for.
          We don't sell your data. Ever.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Quiz Data</h2>
        <p>
          All quiz processing happens <strong class="text-text">in your browser</strong>.
          Your answers are stored temporarily in your browser's localStorage so you can
          resume if you close the tab. They are never sent to our servers. When you
          clear your browser data, your quiz answers are deleted.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Email Collection</h2>
        <p>
          If you choose to enter your email address (for quiz results or our newsletter),
          we store it securely and use it only to send you:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Your detailed quiz results (if requested)</li>
          <li>Our newsletter (if subscribed)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">
          You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in every email. We never sell,
          rent, or share your email address with third parties.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          We use privacy-friendly analytics that do not use cookies or track you
          across websites. We collect anonymous, aggregated data such as page views
          and referral sources to understand how people use the site. No personal
          data is collected through analytics.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          This website does not use tracking cookies. The only data stored in your
          browser is your quiz progress (via localStorage), which you can clear at
          any time through your browser settings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We use the following third-party services:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
          <li><strong class="text-text">Vercel</strong> — website hosting</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">Google Fonts</strong> — typography (loaded from Google's CDN)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact us at
          <strong class="text-text">privacy@isitaudhd.com</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
